damaged during the civil war to turn out various kinds of
necessities and streamline its technology to meet the new
situation of world markets, and it is on this very basis that
Portugal will start new cooperation to help promote the
development of Angola's industry, said the Portuguese minister.
</P>
<P>
At the invitation of Industry Minister Manuel Duque, Mateus
will make extensive contacts with leaders of the economic circle
here, tour enterprises in the capital and take part in the forum
"Investment Opportunities in Angola and the Prospect of
Portuguese Business". 
