<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 14 (Xinhua) -- Texas Governor George W. Bush
said Monday in Austin, Texas, that he will answer questions about
a possible presidential bid when he makes his formal announcement
for re-election this fall.
</P>
<P>
