not yet made a formal announcement. The governor is high on the
list of Republicans who have been touted for the Republican
presidential ticket in the year 2000.
</P>
<P>
Asked about the presidential race, Bush said, "There will be an
appropriate time. It would be at the formal announcement, and I
suspect the first hand raised will be the famous future question,
and I'll give you the answer then." 
