today.
</P>
<P>
Total market volume stood at 121.64 million units, worth 266.35
million Singapore dollars (about 184.97 million U.S. dollars).
Declines continued to overwhelm advances by 259 to 63, while 306
other counters remained unchanged.
</P>
<P>
