cents to end at 20.1 Singapore dollars. Asean Fund and local car
distributor Cycle &AMP; Carriage (C&AMP;C) fell 60 cents each to close at
15.5 US dollars and 13.2 Singapore dollars respectively. The
Development Bank of Singapore (DBS) Foreign and Sea View finished
40 cents lower at 18.4 and 10.9 Singapore dollars respectively.
