Subiakto Tjakrawerdaya said at the seminar that participants of
the conference are also expected to produce an agreement to set up
a market information center for cooperatives and small firms in
Asia-Pacific Countries.
</P>
<P>
The center, he said, will provide information on business
opportunities available for cooperatives and business firms, and
also on their new products.
</P>
<P>
Cooperatives and small firms in Indonesia are frequently dubbed
as one of the country's economic pillars.
</P>
<P>
Data show that the number of cooperatives in Indonesia reached
48,391 in 1996.  
