military alliance with the Moro Islamic Liberation Front (MILF)
and is being reinforced by MILF members.
</P>
<P>
The MILF is a renegade faction of the mainstream rebel group,
the Moro National Liberation Front which signed a peace agreement
with the government last year.
</P>
<P>
The government and the MILF are trying to rescue their
deadlocked peace talks after dozens of MILF rebels were killed
recently in the fierce offensives launched by government troops.
 
