the first black man to win a Grand Slam title when he took the
1968 US Open. He won 33 career titles, including the 1970
Australian Open and 1975 Wimbledon crowns.
</P>
<P>
The stadium was named for Ashe last February, but only after a
USTA plan to sell naming rights was protested by top players.
