<HEADLINE> Opening of Jewish Games Marred by Bridge Accident </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, July 14 (Xinhua) -- The opening of the 15th Maccabee
Games, the Jewish Olympics, near Tel Aviv was struck by disaster
Monday when a bridge to the stadium collapsed, police said.
</P>
<P>
According to Israeli television, the accident killed several
people and injured many more. 
</P>
